document_data.mainbody: The '''Western Wet''' was the sister road of the [[Eastern Wet]], both located in the [[Baldur's Gate/Lower City|Lower City]] of [[Baldur's Gate]] and encircled the city's wharves and docks on the [[Gray Harbor]].
document_data.Location: The Western Wet stretched from the Seatower of Balduran in the [[Baldur's Gate/Seatower|Seatower]] district, passed [[Black Eel Street]] and [[Glaezel's Dock]], continued on to cross [[Caundorl Street]] and [[Hethkantle's Jetty]], and ended by the [[Water Queen's House]].
